Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 08 of Thoracic MRI
When I select 'Bronchial carcinoma' radio button
Then 'T-stage' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'N-stage' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pleural mesothelioma' radio button 
Then 'T-stage' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'N-stage' dropdown menu is enabled
